Package gov.va.isaac.mojos.dbBuilder

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClassifierMojo
    Mojo for running classifier.
    DBBuilder
    Goal which loads a database from an eConcept file, and generates the indexes.
    GenerateUsersMojo
    Goal which processes a users.xml file which is formatted according to the UserGenerationSchema.xsd stored in otf-util.
    InfoModelMetadata
    Goal which creates information model refset metadata in the ISAAC environment
    MojoConceptSpec
    MojoConceptSpec A class that Maven can utilize to create a real ConceptSpec from snippits in our pom.xml files.
    PathBuilder
    Goal which sets up the path within the ISAAC environment
    Setup
    Goal which opens (and creates if necessary) an OTF Versioning Store DB.
    Shutdown
    Goal which shuts down an open data store.
    ValidateConfigurationMojo
    ValidateConfigurationMojo Validate that all of the required user specified configuration information is present, and schema valid.
